Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:39.72,Main,Gaius,0,0,0,,E inutil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:43.85,Main,Gaius,0,0,0,,Însemnul meu nu poate deveni mai puternic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:49.86,Italics,Gaius,0,0,0,,Primul meu însemn e specializat în creație.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:53.18,Italics,Gaius,0,0,0,,Al doilea e specializat în putere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:56.99,Italics,Gaius,0,0,0,,Al treilea e specializat în tragere rapidă.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:00.17,Italics,Gaius,0,0,0,,Dacă vreau să devin mai puternic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:04.66,Italics,Gaius,0,0,0,,trebuie să obțin al patrulea însemn, cel mai util în luptă.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:08.63,Main,Gaius,0,0,0,,Însemnul apare la naștere și nu poate fi schimbat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:10.43,Italics,Gaius,0,0,0,,Ceea ce înseamnă că...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:22.97,Strongest Sage,Onscreen,0,0,0,,Cel mai puternic înțelept, cu cel mai slab însemn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:27.98,Episode Title,Onscreen,0,0,0,,Episodul 1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:27.98,Episode Title,Onscreen,0,0,0,,Cel mai puternic înțelept își face apariția.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:40.79,Main,Peddler,0,0,0,,Vom ajunge curând în capitală.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:45.33,Main,Peddler,0,0,0,,E impresionant că ți-ai părăsit casă și vrei să dai examenul de admitere la doar doisprezece ani.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:49.56,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Sunt hotărât să intru la academie și să devin puternic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.51,Main,Peddler,0,0,0,,E mai bine s-o iei încet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:53.91,Main,Peddler,0,0,0,,You might have been a big fish \Nwhere you came from,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:55.68,Main,Peddler,0,0,0,,dar însemnul tău...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:59.28,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,E un monstru în apropiere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:00.68,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Se îndreaptă spre noi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:01.73,Main,Peddler,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.15,Main,Peddler,0,0,0,,Pare să fie unul destul de mare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:06.10,Main,Peddler,0,0,0,,De câteva ori mai mare decât căruța dumneavoastră.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.98,Main,Peddler,0,0,0,,Spui niște lucruri foarte ciudate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:13.70,Main,Peddler,0,0,0,,That would make it \Na calamity-grade monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:24.03,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Dispatch successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:31.00,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Easily handled with just Enhance Physique \Nand Sunder Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.87,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Exact cum era de așteptat de la capitală...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.75,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,E complet diferită de locul meu natal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.86,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Sabia prietenei mele s-a stricat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.36,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Mi-ați putea face una la fel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.54,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,Nu mai țipa! Te aud și dacă vorbești normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.40,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Îmi cer scuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:09.16,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,But see... She broke her magic sword \Nwhile protecting me from a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.60,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,Magic sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.91,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,And you want me to remake a magic sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.17,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,Nu poți vorbi serios!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:18.00,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Nu poți face nimic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.15,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,Mă tem că nu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.37,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,These weapons are well made...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.30,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Though the enchantments are poorly applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:26.49,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Are there any other swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:28.35,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,It simply can't be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:30.07,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:32.07,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,The entrance exams are tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:33.88,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,If I don't get her a sword, she'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:37.52,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,If you need it that fast, \Nyou might have better luck elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:41.17,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,It's not as if I can forge \Na magic sword by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:43.11,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,We've tried everyone else already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.50,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,Would one of our ready-made swords do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:47.08,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.24,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,It should be about this long,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:53.20,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,and light enough that a girl can swing it \Naround like this with one hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:58.77,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,A sword like that \Ncertainly would have to be enchanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:01.07,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,But it won't be easy to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.68,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,I can handle the enchantment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.11,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,You can?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:08.68,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,Look, kid... \NI get that you want to show off...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:12.39,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,But it can't be done, \Nand she needs to accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:17.27,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,It's true that my fourth crest \Nisn't well suited to enchantments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.88,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,But I think I can handle \Na basic magic sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.68,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,Isn't that the Crest of Failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:24.78,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,All the more impossible, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.96,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Make me a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.41,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,One with a setting for a magistone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.50,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,Wait, you mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.94,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,I'm going to put my faith in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.48,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.71,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,If he fails, the sword will be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.45,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,but you'll have wasted a magistone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.99,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,I still think he can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.51,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,I've got good instincts \Nabout these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:51.18,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Let's get on that enchantment, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:58.23,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:01.86,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,I'm Alma. Alma Lepucius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.52,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,I didn't want my parents \Nmarrying me off to some weirdo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.24,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,so I set off on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:10.65,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,I'm Matthias. Matthias Hildesheimer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:12.16,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,You can call me "Matty."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:15.37,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Sure! It's a pleasure, Matty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.76,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Oh, right! I've got a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:22.47,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,The sword is hers. \NWe left home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.26,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Alma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:26.06,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Speak of the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:26.88,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Lurie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.97,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Alma. Did you have any luck \Nat this shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.72,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Sh-She's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:36.92,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,I'm afraid every shop I tried \Nturned me down...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.54,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,It simply might not be possible \Nto make a magic sword by tomo—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.83,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Oh, this guy? He's Matty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:45.87,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,He said he'd enchant a sword for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.70,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,A-Allow me to introduce myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.71,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,I am humbly referred to \Nas Matthias Hildesheimer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:52.08,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Where'd the formality come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.73,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Was my introduction that off-putting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:59.25,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,This is what I get \Nfor never having friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:01.90,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Lurie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.97,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,I-I'm Lurie Abendroth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.99,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,I'm neither engaged \Nnor romantically involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:11.47,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,You may call me "Lurie," if you wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:13.76,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,"Romantically involved"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.35,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:21.44,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,I had no idea it was customary here \Nto reveal your relationship status.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.32,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,It's all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.05,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,I'll begin the enchantment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.96,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Could you hand me the magistone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.64,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,You can do it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.45,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,It won't take that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:36.57,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,I'm going to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:38.21,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,P-Please do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:43.40,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,The only way to make something this long \Nand light sturdy enough for live combat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.55,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,is to add Enhance Fortitude \Nand Sunder Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.51,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.46,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Here, try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:54.64,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,That was fast! \NIs it really enchanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:57.47,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,There's no way he could do it that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:00.74,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Yeah, isn't it supposed to take way longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:03.34,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,And he didn't even recite an incantation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:06.00,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Let me try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.82,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,It's easy enough to tell if an enchantment—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.72,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,The enchantment worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.45,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,That's crazy sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.27,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,And it took him just moments...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.13,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,What trickery is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:24.08,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,It's just a standard enchantment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.54,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,That's anything but "standard"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:29.49,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Who in the world are you, Matty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.93,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be possible \Nto enchant a sword that quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:36.77,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,But the sword has clearly been enchanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.44,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,and you didn't recite an incantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.02,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,As I forged that sword myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.73,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,I'd know whether you swapped it out \Nwith sleight-of-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.87,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,The only possible conclusion is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.16,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:48.28,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:54.88,Main,Blacksmith,0,0,0,,You wanna become an enchanter, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.35,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:01.04,Main,ExaminerA,0,0,0,,The practical skills exam will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.16,Main,ExaminerA,0,0,0,,Fields tested will include \Nswordsmanship and casting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:03.96,Main,All,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:07.22,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Matty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:12.10,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,You're taking entrance exams, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.54,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:16.74,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,The tactics portion was way too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.74,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,I did just fine in every other subject...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.66,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Alma, Matty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:26.10,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Let's work together to pass the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:27.00,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.48,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,'Kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.35,Main,Lukas,0,0,0,,You're wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.46,Main,Lukas,0,0,0,,You're doing quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:41.71,Main,Lukas,0,0,0,,But can you dodge this next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.59,Main,Lukas,0,0,0,,S-S-Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.34,Main,Lukas,0,0,0,,I surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.66,Main,Lukas,0,0,0,,Where did you get that sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:53.84,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,I did it, Matty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.81,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Lurie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:57.97,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done it \Nwithout that magic sword you made me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.38,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:01.89,Main,ExaminerA,0,0,0,,Next up, Matthias Hildesheimer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.38,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Seems to be my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:06.35,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Give it your best, Matty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.73,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:10.54,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Wait, where's the examiner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:12.85,Main,Guile,0,0,0,,Matthias Hildesheimer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:17.12,Main,Guile,0,0,0,,I hear you're the one \Nwho enchanted Lurie Abendroth's sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.21,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,And? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.69,Main,Guile,0,0,0,,You'll need more than an examiner, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.41,Main,Guile,0,0,0,,I'll fight you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:28.22,Main,Guile,0,0,0,,I'd like to see \Nwhat your father Castor taught you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:30.38,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,You know my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.78,Main,Guile,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.57,Main,Guile,0,0,0,,If you handle yourself \Nwell enough against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:36.59,Main,Guile,0,0,0,,I'll vouch for you to pass, \Nregardless of your other test scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.29,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.35,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,His stance leaves him wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.56,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,He thinks he's taking it easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:50.86,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,That's also why he said, \N"If you handle yourself well enough."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.01,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,I feel a bit insulted...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.16,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,This is a test!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:58.07,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Its purpose is to show them \Nwhat I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:01.97,Main,Guile,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:04.16,Main,Guile,0,0,0,,A boy your age, parrying my strike...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.16,Main,Guile,0,0,0,,I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:17.55,Main,ExaminerA,0,0,0,,Captain of the Knights' Order, Guile, lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.22,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Wow! Isn't he great, Lurie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.03,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:24.10,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Although it happened so quickly \NI couldn't quite follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:28.10,Main,ExaminerD,0,0,0,,Next, we'll conduct the casting exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.19,Main,ExaminerD,0,0,0,,Lurie Abendroth. Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.20,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:35.48,Main,ExaminerD,0,0,0,,Please attack all five targets \Nwith Fire Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.55,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Magic of flame that dwells within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:45.18,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Pierce my foe in the form of an arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.42,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Lurie! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.05,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Incanted casting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:55.06,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,As the name suggests, \Nit's a method for casting spells
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.83,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,through the recitation of particular words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.48,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Anyone can use it regardless of ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:03.20,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,but it offers a poor conversion rate \Non the user's magic power,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:06.08,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,and you're vulnerable \Nto attacks mid-chant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.87,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,They're not ideal for combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.66,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,I'd thought the practice \Nwas long dead, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.06,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.94,Main,Student1,0,0,0,,That's the Crest of Glory! \NWhat an elite!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.37,Main,Student2,0,0,0,,Wish I'd been born \Nwith the Crest of Glory, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.92,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,But in this day and age,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.95,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,the first crest, which is highly compatible \Nwith incanted casting,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.54,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,is labeled the "Crest of Glory"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:27.96,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,and considered the best crest \Nfor magical combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.06,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.68,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,My fourth crest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:37.42,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Excuse me. \NIs Fire Arrow the only spell allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:42.05,Main,ExaminerD,0,0,0,,Not necessarily, \Nbut it's the most basic spell, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:44.54,Main,ExaminerD,0,0,0,,You've got the Crest of Failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.88,Main,ExaminerD,0,0,0,,but if you do well in the other subjects, \Nyou might still pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:50.23,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,As long as I destroy the targets, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.79,Main,ExaminerD,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:55.66,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,"Crest of Failure" casting \Nhas extremely limited range.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:58.73,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,I don't think I could even reach a third \Nof the way to the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:03.36,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,You might want to stand \Na bit farther away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:04.30,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.16,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.37,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,I can assign it limited directionality,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.20,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,but it won't be free of collateral damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:14.08,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,H-How is he casting? \NHe didn't recite an incantation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.96,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Could it be... a wordless spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:18.35,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Wordless casting is in decline,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:21.47,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,and the fourth crest is scorned \Nas the Crest of Failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.72,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,That's the status quo in this day and age!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.50,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.34,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,I might have overdone it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.24,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,It fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.60,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Hey, Matty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.63,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,She looks beautiful \Nin her uniform, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.56,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,What's up, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.43,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Oh, I just—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.60,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Uh, we'd better hurry if we want \Nto make the opening ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:16.77,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,The headmaster will now say a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.77,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,I'm Eduard, the headmaster here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:23.51,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,I despise long speeches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.92,Main Top,Alma,0,0,0,,He's the headmaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:27.21,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,As far as I'm concerned, \Nformality is for First Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:30.43,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Here at my Second Academy, \Nability is everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:34.79,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,We don't care about lineage or crest \Nthe way First Academy does!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:38.71,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Work on those skills, rookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.67,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,That is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:42.42,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,That certainly was short!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.25,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,I almost forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.63,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Matthias Hildesheimer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:50.61,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Drop by my office when this is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:56.05,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Why would the headmaster be calling for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:58.21,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Because I destroyed the grounds \Nduring the exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.47,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Is he going to expel me \Non my first day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.75,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,But I did use a spell \Nto repair the damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.61,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Come in already, Matthias.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.34,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:16.25,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,I knew it...\NHe's—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.75,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Matthias Hildesheimer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.96,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,You defeated the Captain of the Knights' Order \Nduring your swordsmanship exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:25.96,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,and effortlessly used wordless spells \Nduring your casting exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:28.80,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Castor being your father \Nexplains it somewhat,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:33.65,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,but I'm sure there's a deeper reason \Nwhy someone your age is so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.88,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,I won't pry as to why that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:38.64,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,But I do want to ask for your aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.24,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,My... aid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:41.29,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:45.02,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,You saw the other students cast \Nincanted spells, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.82,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.13,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Why do they use \Nsuch an inefficient technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:51.17,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Wouldn't wordless spells be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.07,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,"Inefficient," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:55.72,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, Matthias,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:59.41,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,wordless spells are a lost casting style.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:01.92,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,As I suspected...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:06.14,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,I don't know that a single other person \Nin this kingdom can still use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:11.76,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,I've been hoping to revive wordless spell \Ntechniques here at Second Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.89,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,and teach them to the students...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.44,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,That sounds like a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:18.37,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,But there's one thing stopping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.25,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,There is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.30,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:22.86,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Our sister academy here in the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.15,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,the First Royal Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:28.36,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,The nobility endorses First Academy's teachings,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.15,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,which have a proven track record.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:35.03,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,We've had no choice \Nbut to follow their curriculum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:37.33,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,What kind of track record?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:40.37,Main,Teach2,0,0,0,,First Academy's published research.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:44.00,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,This is their "track record"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.82,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,But it talks only about incanted spells...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:51.30,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Incanted spells are the only form \Nof casting accepted in academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:54.26,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Wordless spells are rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.80,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,How do we get them accepted?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:59.36,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,We'll have to prove the power \Nof wordless casting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:03.69,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,at the next inter-school competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:07.48,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,And that's the "aid" \Nyou're asking me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.34,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:12.65,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,I want you to instruct us \Nin wordless casting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.69,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Matthias.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.33,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.14,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:28.14,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,We will now begin the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:31.00,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,Today, we'll be learning wordless spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:32.46,Main,Student1,0,0,0,,"Wordless spells"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.58,Main Top,Crowd,0,0,0,,Wordless...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:34.71,Main,Student2,0,0,0,,I didn't know there was such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:34.71,Main Top,Crowd,0,0,0,,Never heard of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:36.61,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,Your doubts are understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:39.45,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,That's why we have \Na special guest instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:41.45,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,He'll be teaching you how they work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:45.75,Main,Girl1,0,0,0,,Isn't he the one who passed the\Nentrance exams at the top of the class?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.76,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Yes, that's our Matty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:49.73,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,You can't take credit for him, Alma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:55.00,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,Matthias, could you demonstrate \Nhow wordless casting works?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.45,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.31,Main,Student4,0,0,0,,Was that wordless casting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:08.70,Main,Student5,0,0,0,,Yeah, I didn't hear an incantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.52,Main,Student6,0,0,0,,He's a Crest of Failure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.67,Main,Studen6,0,0,0,,You don't think \Nhe's really a demon, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:16.77,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,Matthias is not the only one \Nwho can use wordless spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:17.83,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,Mr. Gaizal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:18.51,Main,Gaizal,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:25.90,Main,Gaizal,0,0,0,,I'm not particularly good at casting myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:30.27,Main,Gaizal,0,0,0,,but Matthias's teachings have gotten me \Nthis far in just one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:33.12,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,Well, let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.03,Main,All,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.86,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Matty, I can do it now, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.18,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,You can?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.31,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Yeah, let me show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.34,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,How do you like my casting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.94,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,You don't have to imitate \Nthe way he grunts, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.05,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,How is it going, Lurie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:55.42,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,I seem to have the feel for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:57.96,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,but I can't shake my\Nincanted casting habits...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:02.36,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,I may have drained the last \Nof my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.71,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,They're all doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:07.74,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,When I see how impressive \Nwordless spells are,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:12.57,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,I'm forced to wonder \Nwhy we ever stopped using them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.30,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:17.57,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Why has wordless casting \Ngone into decline?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.14,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Matty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:20.80,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:22.56,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Hold out your hand, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.64,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:27.89,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,M-Matty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:32.90,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,W-Well, I have to do this \Nto transfer my magic to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:35.50,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Y-You can transfer magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:36.46,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:39.63,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,I'm using a spell \Nthat attunes my magic to a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:42.18,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,It's typically used \Nfor enchantments, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.79,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Enchantments...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.86,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.78,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,I finally did it, Matty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.31,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,That's the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:55.85,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,And so I taught wordless casting \Nto all the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:58.40,Main Top,Crowd,0,0,0,,Let's show 'em \Nwhat Second Academy can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:58.01,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,A month passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.71,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,It's finally time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:03.21,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,I hope there are \Nno magical chosen ones this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:05.00,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,"Magical chosen ones"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:07.77,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,That's what they call leaders \Nat First Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.27,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,with extremely strong casting ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:11.95,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Any year it seems \NSecond Academy might win,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.87,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,one of these "magical chosen ones" appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:18.66,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,I believe the last Captain of the \NMages' Order was one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.34,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,It seems there is one here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:24.80,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,With roughly ten times my own magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:27.04,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Ten times your power, Matty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.62,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,That's demon-level power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:30.77,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:34.74,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Demons and humans are\Nnatural enemies, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:36.11,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,They certainly are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:39.08,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Demons are the greatest threat \Nto humanity there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:43.20,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Even the court magicians working together \Nprobably couldn't beat one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.30,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,But why would you ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.74,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Oh, just curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.04,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Demons, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:53.75,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,So they've survived into this era...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:57.63,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,Well, looky here! \NA Crest of Failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.93,Main,Leisis,0,0,0,,A Crest of Failure, all by his lonesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:04.37,Main,Giaas,0,0,0,,Hey, no buddies with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:07.05,Main,Giaas,0,0,0,,Did they all run away scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.61,Main,GuyA,0,0,0,,Hey, Crest of Failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:11.48,Main,GuyA,0,0,0,,Cower before the might of Devilis, \Nmagical chosen one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:15.73,Main,First Academy Teach,0,0,0,,Headmaster, I believe Second Academy \Nhas given up on victory entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:18.36,Main,Facus,0,0,0,,That'll be sixty-five wins in a row for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.62,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,Please, Matthias!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:24.32,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,What, no witty rejoinder?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:28.84,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,Has my chosen one Crest of Glory \Nfrightened you into submission?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:30.79,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.58,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,He's not human at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.04,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,He's a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:38.25,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,He's just using a disguise spell \Nto hide his true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:41.76,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,He even has a fake crest \Nto let him walk among humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:47.00,Main,Judge,0,0,0,,The 65th Inter-Academy Competition \Nwill now commence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:48.85,Main,Judge,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.77,Main,Leisis/Giaas,0,0,0,,Magic of flame that dwells within me—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:01.22,Main,Judge,0,0,0,,L-Leisis and Giaas are both out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:04.32,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:06.03,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,Magic of flame that dwells—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.13,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.95,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,He activated the spell \Nbefore he started his chant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.91,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,What? Did he just cast before he—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.60,Main Top,Crowd,0,0,0,,Get him, Devilis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:15.23,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,He did the same with his guard spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.62,Main,Teach1,0,0,0,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.85,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,In other words, \Nhe's just been pretending to chant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:21.30,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,...arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.33,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,The demon's head is its weak point!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:27.74,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Forget your incantation again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:29.55,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,Come, flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.12,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,That proves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:34.94,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,A spell-casting demon, \Npretending to use incantations...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:38.56,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,The demons are the ones \Nthat brought wordless casting into decline!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:44.13,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,The demons want humans' spells \Nas weak as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:47.22,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,They must have infiltrated \NFirst Academy long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:51.70,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,and arranged to have the fourth crest \Ndeclared the Crest of Failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:56.56,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,Come, flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:58.46,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.29,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,How can you be so strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:03.87,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Maybe you're just lousy at fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:11.45,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:15.89,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,D-Did you just use a Spell Shatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:17.17,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:21.69,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,And I tacked on a Magic Veil, \Nso you wouldn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:24.36,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Hey, is that—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:26.01,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Is Devilis...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:27.95,Main,Man,0,0,0,,What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:27.95,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:31.51,Main,Facus,0,0,0,,A-Are you telling me... \NDevilis is a demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:32.95,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Contact the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:34.66,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Evacuate the students at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:35.99,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,A-Ajutor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:38.96,Main Top,Crowd,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:37.50,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Well, what's your next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:40.80,Main,Devil,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:47.85,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,A retreating demon will use \Na Full Flight spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:51.93,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,It will take him about 1.5 seconds \Nfrom spreading his wings to takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:53.76,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,0.8 seconds for my enchantment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:55.65,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,0.7 seconds remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.65,0:22:56.97,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Easily done!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:00.06,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,Now it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:07.94,Main,Eduard,0,0,0,,Did he defeat that demon... \Nall by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:10.95,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,I can't believe there are demons \Ninfiltrating the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:15.55,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,I thought I drove them \Nto the brink of destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:18.41,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,in my old life as Gaius the Sage...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:24.32,Italics,Matt,0,0,0,,It seems there are serious problems \Nin this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:26.95,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,Pop quiz, Alma!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:28.52,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,What's the best crest for enchantment?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:29.63,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Crest of Glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:30.63,Main,Lurie,0,0,0,,And for power?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:31.23,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Crest of Standard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:33.86,Main,Alma,0,0,0,,Now, Matty, say all the crests \Nthree times fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:34.51,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Ce?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:36.32,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Crest of Glory, Crest of Standard, \NCrest of Lesser, Crest of Failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:38.24,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Crest of Glory, Crest of Standard, \NCrest of Lesser, Crest of Failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:39.98,sign_33974_459_Episode_2__The_S,sign,0,0,0,,Episodul 2 \NCel mai puternic înțelept intră în temniță.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.24,0:23:40.32,Main,Matt,0,0,0,,Crest of Glory, Crest of Standard, \NCrest of Lesser... argh!
